OL,3,CLarge fire breaks out in Port Talbot
OL,4,Cinvolving 200 tonnes of commercial
OL,5,Cwaste
OL,7,FA large fire involving 200 tonnes of
OL,8,Fcommercial waste has broken out in
OL,9,FPort Talbot.
OL,11,FMid & West Wales Fire & Rescue Service
OL,12,Fhave confirmed several rescue service
OL,13,Fcrews are currently responding to the
OL,14,Fincident on Dock Road.
OL,16,FCrews from Port Talbot, Neath,
OL,17,FMorriston, Ammanford, Tumble,
OL,18,FCarmarthen, Pontarddulais and
OL,19,FGlynneath Fire Stations were called
OL,20,Fjust after 3.30pm on Wednesday (29
OL,21,FApril) to respond the incident.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
