OL,3,CLarge fire breaks out in Port Talbot
OL,4,Cinvolving 200 tonnes of commercial
OL,5,Cwaste
OL,7,FAs a precaution, local residents have
OL,8,Fbeen advised to keep windows and doors
OL,9,Fclosed if there is thick smoke in the
OL,10,Farea.
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police has also advised to
OL,13,Favoid the area and use alternative
OL,14,Froutes where possible.
OL,16,FThe incident is currently ongoing.
